---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Roadmap | Wolvec"
  description="Where Wolvec is going, a directional view of what we're building toward, updated as we learn from coaches in early access."
>
  <main class="pt-32 pb-24 px-6 min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Where Wolvec is going</h1>
      <p class="text-neutral-400 text-lg mb-16 leading-relaxed">
        We ship in public and we plan in public. Here's what we're building toward.
      </p>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Phase 1: The platform</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          An AI version of you that coaches your clients. One structured conversation builds it,
          no existing content library required. It generates programs grounded in how you
          actually coach, handles day-to-day questions, and runs check-ins in your style.
        </p>
        <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Underneath it, a real coaching platform. Nearly 1,400 exercises with animated
          demonstrations. A program builder you can take over at any point, swap exercises,
          adjust sets and reps, restructure a week, or start from scratch. Supersets, circuits,
          AMRAP, and timed work. Reusable templates. Progress tracking with logged sets, exercise
          history, body metrics, and progress photos.
        </p>
        <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          You decide how much the AI handles, on a three-tier scale (Off, Draft, Auto), and you
          can change it anytime. PAR-Q+ health screening, a coach acknowledgment gate before
          training begins, and hard safety escalation for any mention of pain, injury, illness,
          or dizziness.
        </p>
        <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
          We are building toward early access with a small group of design partner coaches.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Phase 2: Conversation that changes the plan</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
          Your client tells your AI they don't have a cable machine today. Your AI pulls real
          alternatives, you approve with one click, and the program updates. Coaching that adapts
          in conversation, without you rewriting anything.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Phase 3: Depth</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
          An AI that gets sharper the longer it works with you. Specialty depth within fitness,
          strength, hypertrophy, endurance, rehab. Deeper personalization over time. A public
          changelog of everything we ship.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Phase 4: Reach</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
          A marketplace that connects clients to verified coaches, built on the trust we earn
          first.
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="border border-white/10 bg-brand-muted rounded-xl p-6 mb-8">
        <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
          We do not commit to dates. The direction is the promise. Pace depends on what we learn
          from coaches in early access.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <a
            href="/#early-access"
            class="inline-block bg-brand-accent hover:bg-brand-accent/90 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-md transition-colors"
          >
            Apply for early access &rarr;
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
